{"tid":1545232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想要831條片既，同我入黎！","createTime":"2019-09-06T00:14:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T01:10:38.000Z","uid":162645,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fc57d64ac954d8c146d9597357bdac98def0caf8","tid":1545232,"uid":162645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T00:14:45.000Z","msg":"時間所剩無幾，今晚就會刪片<br />\n要攞到條片，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">只有靠 循法律途徑 去告警隊/黨鐵</span><br />\n令到條片成為證據，咁先可以保住條片！<br />\n<br />\n之前和理飛2.0 咁成功，全靠呂麗乳搖 巴打洗post<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我要你地全部 化身 呂麗乳搖！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nh73ris.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnh73ris.jpg&h=b79261fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（其他文宣都ok，不過要有法律熱線）<br />\n<br />\n將呢張相 洗到全連登，全香港都係！<br />\n目標就係要搵到當晚太子站既人 企出黎！<br />\n<br />\n其實唔一定要係發夢既人報警，<br />\n只要當時係現場既路人/市民，<br />\n都可以先由法律行動保住條片<br />\n<br />\n參考：前法庭書記睹警太子站毆乘客疑患PTSD　向警務處長索償5000元<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190903/s00001/1567506284957/【逃犯條例-831】前法庭書記睹警太子站毆乘客疑患ptsd-向警務處長索償5000元\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190903%2Fs00001%2F1567506284957%2F%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-831%E3%80%91%E5%89%8D%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD%E6%9B%B8%E8%A8%98%E7%9D%B9%E8%AD%A6%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99%E6%AF%86%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E7%96%91%E6%82%A3ptsd-%E5%90%91%E8%AD%A6%E5%8B%99%E8%99%95%E9%95%B7%E7%B4%A2%E5%84%9F5000%E5%85%83&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H4uQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=61cc2662\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190903%2Fs00001%2F1567506284957%2F%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-831%E3%80%91%E5%89%8D%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD%E6%9B%B8%E8%A8%98%E7%9D%B9%E8%AD%A6%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99%E6%AF%86%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E7%96%91%E6%82%A3ptsd-%E5%90%91%E8%AD%A6%E5%8B%99%E